node.text:
Too often people take on more responsibilities than required, which can hurt relationships (even though you were just trying to help the relationship) and hurt your mental health. If you’ve been finding yourself extra irritable or angry at others lately maybe it’s time to reevaluate what you are taking on and what you can let go of? If you’ve been feeling burnt out and depressed, maybe it’s time to release some responsibility that is not for you to carry?

You are responsible for your healing & happiness.
